  * Potential microformat profiles to include:
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/rel-license" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/rel-nofollow" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/rel-home" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/h-resume" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/h-card" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/h-adr" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://microformats.org/profile/h-event" rel="profile" />`
  * Other profiles
    * `<link href="http://www.w3.org/2005/11/profile" rel="profile" />`
    * `<link href="http://gmpg.org/xfn/11" rel="profile" />`
  * [ProfilePage on schema.org](http://schema.org/ProfilePage)
    `<html lang="en" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ProfilePage">`
  * [Open Graph Protocol](https://ogp.me/) `<head prefix="og: http://ogp.me/ns# profile: http://ogp.me/ns/profile#">`
    * `<meta property="og:site_name" content="Mark Morga" />`
    * `<meta property="og:type" content="profile" />`
    * `<meta property="og:locale" content="en_US" />`
    * `<meta property="og:see_also" itemprop="sameAs" content="https://markmorga.com/resume" />`
    * `<meta property="og:url" itemprop="url" content="https://markmorga.com/resume" />`
    * `<meta property="profile:first_name" content="Mark" />`
    * `<meta property="profile:last_name" content="Morga" />`
    * `<meta property="profile:username" content="markmorga" />`
    * `<meta property="profile:gender" content="male" />`
* Images for icons, etc.
